- **Documentation index:** `docs/guides/README.md` · `docs/README.md` · **Monorepo:** `docs/monorepo.md` · **Sites:** `docs/sites.md`
- **Enter transitions:** `docs/guides/transition_guide.md` + `scripts/chrome/slide-transitions.js`
- **Deck progress bar:** `docs/guides/style_guide.md` §4.5 + **`styles/style-guide/01-tokens-base.css`** (`.reveal .progress`, `.deck-progress-thumb`, `.is-dragging`, `.is-snapping`, `--deck-progress-bar-*`, `--deck-progress-thumb-pct`, `--deck-progress-s-mask`) + `shared/scripts/slide-progress.js` (v8+) — **always on**; **bar gradient centered on S** (dark gray ends → dark magenta mid → theme magenta peak slightly brighter than S thumb at `--sfk-magenta-light`); Reveal fill `span` stays transparent; hover peek; **smooth drag** (visual-only thumb follow, no slide jump during drag); **release snap** to nearest slide fraction via easeOutCubic ~220ms then `Reveal.slide()`; key fns: `setThumbFraction`, `snapToNearestSlide`, `nearestSlideIndex`; S thumb uses `assets/logos/S.png` as mask with brand magenta gradient tint. Skill: `.cursor/skills/deck-progress-bar/SKILL.md`.
- **Bottom-right nav cluster:** `docs/guides/style_guide.md` §4.3 + **`01-tokens-base.css`** (`.deck-nav-cluster`) + `scripts/core/deck-nav.js` — `bindDeckNavCluster()` after `Reveal.initialize()`; page number `c/t` centered between left/right arrows; arrow visuals unchanged.
- **Wheel navigation:** `docs/guides/WHEEL_NAV_GUIDE.md` + `shared/scripts/slide-wheel-nav.js` — custom two-tick scroll flip; `document` capture phase; `SlideWheelNav.bind()` after `Reveal.initialize()` (see `scripts/core/deck-reveal.js`). Interactive zones must **not** call `stopPropagation` on `wheel` (only pointer events + Reveal nav keys). Optional `blur()` after button clicks in games/pickers.
- **Portrait adapt (strategy A):** `docs/guides/PORTRAIT_ADAPT_GUIDE.md` + **`styles/style-guide/10-portrait-adapt.css`** + `shared/scripts/portrait-deck-adapt.js` — `PortraitDeckAdapt.init()` before `initReveal`, `bind(Reveal)` after initialize; `html.deck-portrait` drives layout fold + safe-area; bottom hint「横屏体验更佳」; does **not** change `getSlideDimensions()`. Skill: `.cursor/skills/portrait-deck-adapt/SKILL.md`. Vertical: `SlideWheelNav` `ignoreWhen: PortraitDeckAdapt.isPortrait`. Disable: `?portrait=0`.
- **Content page title zone (top-left H2 + top-right Logo):** `docs/guides/style_guide.md` §4.4 + **`01-tokens-base.css`** / **`04a-content-header.css`** (tokens & `.slide-page-header` H2 band) + `scripts/core/deck-viewport.js` — `injectSlideBrandLogos()` injects corner logo; `fitSlidePageTitles()` binary-searches max font size on init / resize / `slidechanged`. Do not hand-tune title `font-size` in HTML/CSS for unified content pages.
